298
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:35,670
if you want to enhance your vision

299
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:38,520
and maintain your vision as you get older.

300
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:42,400
And again, if you're a
15-year-old or a 12-year-old,

301
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,970
this episode is especially for you,

